== 經貿關係 ==
中國於2009年成為巴西的最大貿易伙伴<ref name="cement" /><ref>Malcolm Moore, [http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/economics/5296515/China-overtakes-the-US-as-Brazils-largest-trading-partner.html China overtakes the US as Brazil's largest trading partner] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/economics/5296515/China-overtakes-the-US-as-Brazils-largest-trading-partner.html |date=20180101194425 }}, The Telegraph, 9 May 2009</ref>。

巴西和中國是一個名為[[金磚國家|金磚國家]]的經濟組織成員，該組織還由俄羅斯、印度和南非組成。中國貢獻了總運營預算的41%。巴西貢獻了18%的運營預算。雙方同意增加新興市場和發展中市場之間的貿易。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/monkey-cage/wp/2014/07/17/what-the-new-bank-of-brics-is-all-about/|title=What the new bank of BRICS is all about|last1=Desai|first1=Raj M.|date=2014-07-17|newspaper=Washington Post|access-date=2018-04-20|last2=Vreeland|first2=James Raymond|language=en-US|issn=0190-8286|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007083712/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/monkey-cage/wp/2014/07/17/what-the-new-bank-of-brics-is-all-about/}}</ref>

据巴西政府统计，2017年中巴双边贸易额达到750亿美元。自2003年至2018年，中国在巴西投资了至少1,240亿美元，主要集中在石油、采矿和能源领域<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/BOLSONARO-BRAZIL-CHINA-20101025/4629540.html |title=博尔索纳罗批评中国的言论使北京对巴西感到紧张 |publisher=美國之音 |date=2018-10-26 |accessdate=2018-10-29 |archive-date=2018-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181029112222/https://www.voachinese.com/a/BOLSONARO-BRAZIL-CHINA-20101025/4629540.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2019年4月的一年內，中國從巴西進口7,100萬噸[[大豆|大豆]]。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2897148 |title=美中貿易戰助長亞馬遜雨林大火？彭博評論這麼說... |work=自由財經 |date=2019-08-27 |accessdate=2019-08-27 |archive-date=2019-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827044237/https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2897148 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2018年，中國（包括香港）是巴西牛肉的最大出口地，佔該年巴西牛肉出口量的44%。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ers.usda.gov/amber-waves/2019/july/brazil-once-again-becomes-the-world-s-largest-beef-exporter/ |title=Brazil Once Again Becomes the World’s Largest Beef Exporter |date=2019-07-01 |website=usda.gov |accessdate=2019-08-30 |archive-date=2019-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823150236/https://www.ers.usda.gov/amber-waves/2019/july/brazil-once-again-becomes-the-world-s-largest-beef-exporter/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

